airgeddon (wireless audit tool)

This is a multi-use bash script for Linux systems to audit wireless
networks.

HOME: https://github.com/v1s1t0r1sh3r3/airgeddon

======================================================================
REQUIRES: aircrack-ng asleap bettercap bully crunch ettercap hashcat hcxdumptool hcxtools hostapd john lighttpd mdk4 pixiewps reaver wireshark 

